resources.string: "Amap Mobile Service: The Service will provide lane matching results to certified navigation software or navigation related fucntion in your device when you start such navigation software, to help such navigation software to provide lane navigation service in specific areas and roads. To provide the lane matching service and satisfy related Chinese Laws, Regulations and National Standards, The Service needs the following permission from the system, and shall not obtain and use your personal information. Location Permission: for lane matching service."
